1. A/C- Scope of work:
1.1 Supply & Install of FAHU unit as per drawings.
1.2 Supply & Install of FCU as per drawings.
1.3 Supply & Install of A/C duct & Ventilation duct.
1.4 Supply & Installation of Fire Rated duct for Basement.
1.5 Supply & Install of Ventilation fan as per drawing.
1.6 Supply & Install of Chilled water pump.
1.7 Supply & installation of Pressurization unit & Chemical dosing.
1.8 Supply & Installation of CHW pipe with insulation.
1.9 Supply & Install of Valves and Control valve.
1.10 Supply and installation of grilles & diffusers.
1.11 Testing and commissioning.
2. Drainage & Water Supply Scope of work:
2.1 Supply & Install all the water supply booster pump & Transfer pump & water circulation pump as per drawings.
2.2 Supply & Install of GRP Roof water tank, Water heater as per drawings.
2.3 Supply & installation of filtration system.
2.4 Supply & Install of water supply pipe.
2.5 Supply & Install UPVC drainage pipe.
2.6 Supply & Installation of submersible pump.
2.7 Supply & Install of Manhole cover, Gully trap cover & floor trap cover as per drawings.
2.8 Supply and installation of below grade UPVC pipe for Basement.
3. Fire Fighting Scope of work:
3.1 Supply & Install all the Fire Fighting pump as per drawing.
3.2 Supply & Install of firefighting pipe as per drawings.
3.3 Supply & installation of Fire hose Cabinet with accessories as per drawing.
3.4 Supply & Install of upright, Pendent and sidewall type sprinkler as per drawing.
3.5 Supply & Installation of clean agent system as per drawings.
3.6 Supply & Installation of Fire extinguisher as per drawing.
4. Electrical & Low Current System
4.1 Supply & Installation of LV Panel and Capacitor bank.
4.2 Supply & Installation of Generator & ATS.
4.3 Supply & Installation of MCC Panel, SMDBs and Final DB's.
4.4 Supply & Installation of Busbar System.
4.5 Supply & Installation of Electrical LV cables & wires.
4.6 Supply & Installation of Isolators.
4.7 Supply & Installation of Light point & switches.
4.8 Supply & Installation of Power point and wiring accessories.
4.9 Supply & Installation of cable trays & accessories.
4.10 Supply & Installation of Earthing system.
4.11 Supply & Installation of Lightning protection system.
4.12 Supply & Installation of Fire alarm, PAVA & CO system.
4.13 Supply & Installation of Emergency Lighting system.
4.14 Supply & Installation of Structured cabling system.
4.15 Supply & Installation of SMATV system (IF).
4.16 Supply & Installation of Intercom system.
4.17 Supply & Installation of Access control system.
4.18 Supply & Installation of CCTV system.
4.19 Supply & Installation of Lighting control system.
4.20 Supply & Installation of Energy monitoring system.
4.21 Supply & Installation of Vehicle charging Equipment.
4.22 Supply of Light Fixtures.
4.23 ADDC Fees.

Exclusion:
1. Any kind of Civil Carpentry and decorative work.
2. Any kind of external works & Foundations.
3. Civil works such as any excavation, back fillings, concrete tiles, warning tape, direction pole, building the manholes,
plater the manholes, install the covers of the manhole, branch the manholes, digging, bedding, tiling, backfilling, warning
tapes & cable route markers, Cutting Chiseling, plastering, painting, welding, coring, wall and slab cutting.
4. Manhole covers, Ducts, Trenches for all incoming Power & Telecommunication services and associated civil works such
as digging, bedding, tiling, backfilling, warning tapes & cable route markers.
5. Boring or drilling works & other associated civil works.
6. Supply and Installation of Temporary Electrical, Water Supply, Drainage and Fire Fighting Works.
7. Supply & fixing of Fire Stopping Joint Sealant at places of MEP services penetrations (such as and Bus Bar Risers & AC
Ducts and water supply & drainage pipe. etc.).
8. All works related to the Swimming pool, Spa, Sauna and Freezer.
9. Any kind of construction of Manhole and valve chamber.
10. Any kind of material shifting to the roof.
11. Any kind of sleeves & openings.
12. Factory witness Test, Third party Testing & Commissioning.
13. Any kind of material shifting to the roof.
14. Any kind of supply of sanitary wares and its accessories.
15. Any kind of supply of mixers and angle valves, flexible hose, and sealant.
16. Any kind supply of water meter box & Water meter.
17. Any kind of irrigation system & Land scaping (only MEP provision).
18. Any kind of Swimming pool equipment (only MEP provision).
19. Wild Air system.
20. Any kind of Natural Gas related work.
21. Supply & Installation of Heat Exchanger with all Accessories and Tabreed Fee.
22. Supply & installation of Temporary Firefighting & Fire Alarm system has been excluded.
23. Any Kind of RCC storage tanks covers.
24. VAT is excluded.
25. Any kind of Govt. Fees, Tabreed Fee, ADCD fee. Third party fee, Estidama fee.
26. Any other items not specifically mentioned in the Consultant specification and Tender drawings.

Required:
1. Electricity, Water Supply and scaffolding for site work.
2. Tower or Mobile crane for lifting machines & all equipment.
3. Wall drilling.
4. Site office.
5. Stores.
6. Telephone & Fax.
